⍝ ReduceNWise.tc
⍝ ══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO dyadic; A simple scalar or one-item integer
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (¯1↓⍴B),(1+(¯1↑⍴B)-|A)
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
